title: Franchise Five: Most Interesting NFC Teams (Football 6/1)
description:
It's Mount Rushmore, with a twist. Over the next two weeks, CBSSports.com is unveiling 'Franchise Fives', highlighting the top members in the history of each NFL team. This week, it's a focus on the NFC. Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough each narrow in on their most interesting 'Franchise Five' in the NFC, breaking down no-brainer picks, some questionable decisions and snubs. The Pick Six Supefriends talk Bucs (6:50), 49ers (23:45), Lions (37:30) and Falcons (46:15).
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
